Title: Thinking back to late 2015 when I started joking 'I can't believe Trump is going to be our next pres...
Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: Thinking back to late 2015 when I started joking 'I can't believe Trump is going to be our next president' and suddenly I don't think my 'In 2027 when this is all over...' jokes are very funny.
